::DarkMouse::

She looked over to see Quickstrike standing near her.
"Yes it is commander.  How are you feeling? You look cleaner.  Oh, I got the 
tunnel finishes.  I even camoflaged the door way and set up scanners in it 
and around it.  You can monitor it at this console.  It you wish, please 
tell Megatron that I followed your instructions to the letter. Oh, I hope I 
didn't cause you any trouble earlier commander.  I'm sorry that I imposed on 
your servisec to help with the tunnel.  You must have been very busy.  I 
will try in the future not to trouble you."
She still looked at him.  He was good looking.  But she knew that she had no 
chance with him.  Not with the other female bots around.

----------Original Message-----------
From: Talon Harvilicz
Date: Fri Jun 23, 2000 5:15pm
Subject: Neo Beast Wars


Quickstrike:


Quickstrike walked to the Predacon's cave, meanwhile he hear the
transmission from Bobertron. All he could do in reply to it was let out a
healthy laugh. He gave no reply to it, just kept his path to the cave. 3rd
in command? He was second in command.

He slowled his pace and looked behind himself to see if Lightmare was still
following. He turned his head back around and kept moving. The
scorpion/cobra made it back to base soon enough, just before the nightfall.
He entered and transformed to robot mode. He stretched his arms out over his
head and tilted his trunk back slightly.

Noticing Dark Mouse, he said, "Nice night ain't it?"
